# Session Summary: Anesthesia Records & PDF Enhancements

This document summarizes the significant improvements and bug fixes implemented to enhance the anesthesia record system, PDF generation, and patient history integration.

## Key Enhancements

### 1. Anesthesia History & UI
- **Unbilled Record Filtering**: Implemented backend filtering in [his_client_final.py](file:///c:/Users/A03772/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/his_client_final.py) to exclude anesthesia records missing a `COST_ID`. This ensures only billed/active records are displayed for patients.
- **Collapsible Materials Section**: Modified [legacy_schedule.html](file:///c:/Users/A03772/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/templates/legacy_schedule.html) to hide the "Medical Materials" section by default within the anesthesia history detail view. Users can now toggle this section to view details, keeping the interface clean.

### 2. Patient Profile & Header
- **ID Number Display**: Updated the patient detail header to display **"身分證字號" (ID Number)** instead of "就診號" (Visit Number) for better identification.

### 3. PDF Generation Fixes
- **Checkbox Mapping (Face Mask/IVGA)**: Fixed an issue where selecting "Face Mask/IVGA" did not check the boxes in the PDF. This was resolved by adding a unique ID to the checkbox and updating the `PDFLib` logic to bypass text-matching issues caused by newlines.
- **Surgery Date Parsing**: Implemented robust date parsing in the PDF generator to correctly handle various date formats (including `YYYYMMDD`), ensuring the **"Expected Surgery Date"** appears correctly on the generated form.

### 4. Inpatient (IPD) Integration
- **Deep Links to HIS**: Added direct links to the external HIS system for inpatient records.
  - **開啟住院紀錄 (Open Inpatient Record)**: Links directly to the medical record page.
  - **開啟住院首頁 (Open Inpatient Homepage)**: Links to the inpatient homepage.
- **Conditional Visibility**: The "Open Inpatient Homepage" link is **automatically hidden** for patients who have already been discharged, preventing access to expired inpatient sessions.

## Verification Results
- ✅ Unbilled records are correctly hidden in patient `003457263J`.
- ✅ PDF checkboxes for "Mask" and "IVGA" are correctly marked.
- ✅ PDF surgery date is correctly populated.
- ✅ Inpatient links are only visible for the appropriate `ADM` record types and handled correctly based on discharge status.

